findings.interpretation: Personnel mediates 10.6% of VIIRS effect on casualties

findings.significance: Personnel does not significantly mediate VIIRS-Casualty relationship
findings.interpretation: VIIRS and personnel may have independent effects on casualties

recommendations: Consider both VIIRS and Personnel as separate predictors (complementary information)
If mediation is strong, Personnel may be redundant with VIIRS
Test reverse mediation (Personnel -> VIIRS -> Casualties) for comparison
Use causal inference methods for stronger claims about mediation
